 Monitor" style=3D"filter: blur(4px);">
                        </a>
                        <p>For those who are struggling with labor shortage=
s and aging equipment, we have a proposal:
                            effortless preventive maintenance.
                        </p>
                        <p>The software "AI Servo Monitor" helps with preve=
ntive maintenance by detecting early signs of
