                    <section>
                        <h2 id=3D"section-2">Effortless Preventive Maintena=
nce</h2>
                        <p>"Effortless Preventive Maintenance" is a mainten=
ance system that utilizes AI servo monitors
                            to automatically detect early signs of equipmen=
t failure and enables efficient maintenance.
                        </p>
                        <p>This approach makes maintenance easy to start, e=
asy to understand, and easy to continue, thus
                            reducing the burden on on-site personnel.</p>

                        <h3 id=3D"section-2-1">Concept of AI Servo Monitor<=
/h3>
                        <a href=3D"https://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/i=
mage/illustration_of_AI_servo_monitor_concept.en.png" data-lightbox=3D"grou=
p">
                            <img class=3D"img-responsive-inline" src=3D"htt=
ps://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/image/illustration_of_AI_servo_monitor_=
concept.en.png" alt=3D"Illustration Representing Data Measurement and Autom=
atic Analysis by AI Servo Monitor" style=3D"filter: blur(4px);">
                        </a>
                        <p>No additional sensors or special programs are re=
quired. The system measures the speed and
                            torque of the drive axis
                            during regular production operations and automa=
tically detects early signs of failure.</p>
                        <p>It is easy to start and can be continued without=
 effort, enabling preventive maintenance of
                            equipment.</p>

                        <h3 id=3D"section-2-2">Breakdown of Detected Failur=
es</h3>
                        <a href=3D"https://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/i=
mage/pie_chart_of_machine_failures_breakdown_found_by_AI_Servo_Monitor_v3.e=
n.png" data-lightbox=3D"group">
                            <img class=3D"img-responsive-inline" src=3D"htt=
ps://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/image/pie_chart_of_machine_failures_bre=
akdown_found_by_AI_Servo_Monitor_v3.en.png" alt=3D"Pie Chart Showing Breakd=
own of Failures Detected by AI Servo Monitor in Factories" style=3D"filter:=
 blur(4px);">
                        </a>
                        <p>Over the past four years, AI Servo Monitor has b=
een used on more than 300 machines in real
                            production. It has detected early signs of fail=
ures that could have led to serious equipment
                            shutdowns.
                        </p>
                        <p>This chart shows the breakdown of 37 early signs=
 of failures detected by AI Servo Monitor.
                        </p>
                        <p>Early inspections and repairs based on these fin=
dings have been beneficial for equipment in
                            actual operation.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Spindle bearing wear and increased spindle =
runout</li>
                            <li>Linear guide damage</li>
                            <li>Ball screw wear</li>
                            <li>Cover deformation</li>
                            <li>Bearing wear on rotating shafts</li>
                            <li>Drive circuit failures (included in =E2=80=
=9COther=E2=80=9D in the chart)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>


                    <section>
                        <h2 id=3D"section-3">How to Use AI Servo Monitor</h=
2>
                        <h3 id=3D"section-3-1">Notifies You Before a Breakd=
own</h3>
                        <a href=3D"https://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/i=
mage/illustration_of_maintenance_improvement_flow_with_AI_servo_monitor.en.=
png" data-lightbox=3D"group">
                            <img class=3D"img-responsive-inline" src=3D"htt=
ps://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/image/illustration_of_maintenance_impro=
vement_flow_with_AI_servo_monitor.en.png" alt=3D"Illustration Showing the M=
aintenance Flow with AI Servo Monitor" style=3D"filter: blur(4px);">
                        </a>
                        <p>When a notification of an early sign of failure =
arrives, perform an inspection of the
                            equipment.
                        </p>
                        <p>There is no need to check the data every day.</p=
>
                        <p>Effective inspections and preventive maintenance=
 aim to extend the lifespan of the equipment.
                        </p>

                        <h3 id=3D"section-3-2">Email Notifications - Unders=
tand Early Signs of Failure and Necessary
                            Actions
                        </h3>
                        <a href=3D"https://www.fanuc.co.jp/en/product/iot/i=
